WWC0014[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written evidence submitted by Newham College[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Underachievement in education by white working-class children[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Introduction [bold]and[bold] details of submitter[bold]&#xa0;
